          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Art Upload Recommendations",
            "row_content": "<p>All file types accepted, vector files are always preferred, raster art should be at least 300 DPI. We work in CMYK and will always do our best to match your requested colors as closely as possible.</p><p><strong>Tip:</strong> If you're using Canva or Procreate, we recommend exporting your documents as PDFs<br/><br/><strong>Minimum Size</strong>: While DTF handles fine details well, elements smaller than 0.02 inches (0.5mm) may not transfer properly</p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_tem7Hj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Build Your Own DTF Transfer",
            "row_content": "<p>Don't have your own design, now you can create your own transfers with our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/ninja-dtf-transfer-builder\" target=\"_blank\">Ninja DTF Transfer Builder</a>.</p>",
