          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Glitter Option",
            "row_content": "<p>Looking to brighten up your designs and make them stand out even more? Glitter is available if you choose our Gang Sheet Builder Option.</p><p><a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/build-your-own-gang-sheet?variant=41169746067539\" title=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/build-your-own-gang-sheet?variant=41169746067539\">Build Your Glitter Gang Sheet Here</a></p>",
